A simple dice wagering game played with bitcoins. 

For each bet, Jackpot Dice will throw a dice, giving you a 1 in 6 chance of winning 400% of your bet. You also have another 1 in 6 change of winning 100% of your bet back! Wagers can any amount from 0.01 BTC up to 1000 BTC.

The site was announced on January 28th, 2011 (1.1) however the payout returns have changed since that announcement.

